    WHERE [l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)

2023-07-30 02:10:01.632 +02:00 [INF] Route matched with {action = "Lessons", controller = "Course", area = "", page = ""}. Executing controller action with signature Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.IActionResult Lessons(Int32) on controller JudgeSystem.Web.Controllers.CourseController (JudgeSystem.Web).
2023-07-30 02:10:01.645 +02:00 [INF] Executing action method JudgeSystem.Web.Controllers.CourseController.Lessons (JudgeSystem.Web) - Validation state: "Valid"
2023-07-30 02:10:01.655 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (10ms) [Parameters=[@__courseId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [l].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [l].[CourseId], [l].[Name], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Problems] AS [p0]
    WHERE [p0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [l].[Id] = [p0].[LessonId]), [l].[Type]
FROM [Lessons] AS [l]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[LessonId]
    FROM [Practices] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[LessonId]
    FROM [Contests] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[StartTime] < GETDATE() AND [c].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
) AS [t0] ON [l].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

SELECT [l].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [l].[CourseId], [l].[Name], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Problems] AS [p0]
    WHERE [p0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [l].[Id] = [p0].[LessonId]), [l].[Type]
FROM [Lessons] AS [l]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[LessonId]
    FROM [Practices] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]

SELECT [c].[EndTime], [c].[LessonId], [t0].[Id], [c].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [c]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [l].[Id]
    FROM [Lessons] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [c].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[LessonId]
    FROM [Practices] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[EndTime] < GETDATE() AND [c].[EndTime] >= DATEADD(day, CAST(@__p_0 AS int), GETDATE())

SELECT [c].[EndTime], [c].[LessonId], [t0].[Id], [c].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [c]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [l].[Id]
    FROM [Lessons] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [c].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[LessonId]
    FROM [Practices] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[EndTime] < GETDATE() AND [c].[EndTime] >= DATEADD(day, CAST(@__p_0 AS int), GETDATE())

) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]

FROM [Contests] AS [c]

FROM [Lessons] AS [l]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[LessonId]
    FROM [Practices] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]
WHERE [l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND ([t].[Id] <> 1 OR ([t].[Id] IS NULL))

2023-07-30 13:11:42.373 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Double)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[EndTime], [c].[LessonId], [t0].[Id], [c].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [c]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [l].[Id]
    FROM [Lessons] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [c].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (

SELECT [c].[EndTime], [c].[LessonId], [t0].[Id], [c].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [c]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [l].[Id]
    FROM [Lessons] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [c].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[LessonId]
    FROM [Practices] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [c].[EndTime] < GETDATE() AND [c].[EndTime] >= DATEADD(day, CAST(@__p_0 AS int), GETDATE())

    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[ActualPoints], [s].[Code], [s].[CompilationErrors], [s].[ContestId], [s].[CreatedOn], [s].[DeletedOn], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedOn], [s].[PracticeId], [s].[ProblemId], [s].[SubmisionDate], [s].[UserId]

    WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [s].[ContestId] = @__contestId_0 AND [s].[UserId] = @__userId_1 AND [s].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_2 AND ((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [e].[SubmissionId]) > 0 OR ([s].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL))
    ORDER BY [s].[SubmisionDate] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_3 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_4 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [p].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [p].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [p].[AutomatedTestingProject], [p].[CreatedOn], [p].[DeletedOn], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[IsExtraTask], [p].[LessonId], [p].[MaxPoints], [p].[ModifiedOn], [p].[Name], [p].[OrderBy], [p].[SubmissionType], [p].[TestingStrategy], [p].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ExecutedTests] AS [e0] ON [t].[Id] = [e0].[SubmissionId]
ORDER BY [t].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[ActualPoints], [s].[Code], [s].[CompilationErrors], [s].[ContestId], [s].[CreatedOn], [s].[DeletedOn], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedOn], [s].[PracticeId], [s].[ProblemId], [s].[SubmisionDate], [s].[UserId]
    FROM [Submissions] AS [s]
    WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [s].[ContestId] = @__contestId_0 AND [s].[UserId] = @__userId_1 AND [s].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_2 AND ((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [e].[SubmissionId]) > 0 OR ([s].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL))
    ORDER BY [s].[SubmisionDate] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_3 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_4 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [p].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [p].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [p].[AutomatedTestingProject], [p].[CreatedOn], [p].[DeletedOn], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[IsExtraTask], [p].[LessonId], [p].[MaxPoints], [p].[ModifiedOn], [p].[Name], [p].[OrderBy], [p].[SubmissionType], [p].[TestingStrategy], [p].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ExecutedTests] AS [e0] ON [t].[Id] = [e0].[SubmissionId]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]

    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[ActualPoints], [s].[Code], [s].[CompilationErrors], [s].[ContestId], [s].[CreatedOn], [s].[DeletedOn], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedOn], [s].[PracticeId], [s].[ProblemId], [s].[SubmisionDate], [s].[UserId]

    ORDER BY [s].[SubmisionDate] DESC

) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]

    OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [p].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [p].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [p].[AutomatedTestingProject], [p].[CreatedOn], [p].[DeletedOn], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[IsExtraTask], [p].[LessonId], [p].[MaxPoints], [p].[ModifiedOn], [p].[Name], [p].[OrderBy], [p].[SubmissionType], [p].[TestingStrategy], [p].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]

FROM (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[ActualPoints], [s].[Code], [s].[CompilationErrors], [s].[ContestId], [s].[CreatedOn], [s].[DeletedOn], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedOn], [s].[PracticeId], [s].[ProblemId], [s].[SubmisionDate], [s].[UserId]
    FROM [Submissions] AS [s]
    WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [s].[ContestId] = @__contestId_0 AND [s].[UserId] = @__userId_1 AND [s].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_2 AND ((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [e].[SubmissionId]) > 0 OR ([s].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL))
    ORDER BY [s].[SubmisionDate] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_3 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_4 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [p].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [p].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [p].[AutomatedTestingProject], [p].[CreatedOn], [p].[DeletedOn], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[IsExtraTask], [p].[LessonId], [p].[MaxPoints], [p].[ModifiedOn], [p].[Name], [p].[OrderBy], [p].[SubmissionType], [p].[TestingStrategy], [p].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ExecutedTests] AS [e0] ON [t].[Id] = [e0].[SubmissionId]
ORDER BY [t].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]
